  "title": "Locum Staff Nurse",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>General nursing duties in clinic which include preparing patients for their health screening.</p><p>Handle any registration, appointment bookings and answer any phone call enquiries</p><p>Follow up with patients on any feedback / concerns that they may have</p><p>Interact and coordinate with different teams to ensure that the centre's operations is running smoothly and\nefficiently</p><p>Provide administrative support to the department when required.</p><p>Any other adhoc duties as assigned by the Clinic Manager</p><p>Recognized qualification in nursing field</p><p>Candidates with blood taking or iv cannulation experience will have added advantage</p><p>At least 2 year(s) of working experience in related field is required for this position with</p><p>Willing to do onsite event.</p><p>Part time</p><p>Must be Registered with valid SNB</p><p>Must be able to perform cannulation</p><p>Applicants who are interested in this role are invited to apply with their comprehensive resume with full details via <strong>\"Apply Now\" </strong>button. Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
